title: Rabbi Marvin Antelman To Eliminate The Opiate vol1
description: To Eliminate The Opiate, by Rabbi Marvin S. Antelman is a 2 Volume book set which contains so much unknown information that one may ask how its possible that a single individual could have retrieved all this. If there's a holy covenant for knowledge and wisdom, Rabbi Antelman must have been carrying it around all his lifetime. A competing organization wich has access to even more "unknown" information, are of course The Jesuits and their Vatican Library. Interesting enough, Antelman barely mentions the Jesuits as the "evil-do-ers" inside his two Volumes
